# Training data — never bake into any image (trainers fetch corpus from S3/DB
# at runtime). These are GBs (datasets .pt + cached videos). Safe for the
# detection build too (it does not COPY ml_pipeline/training/). Do NOT add
# ml_pipeline/models/ here — the detection image COPYs weights from it.
ml_pipeline/training/datasets/
ml_pipeline/training/_dataset_cache/
ml_pipeline/training/labels/
ml_pipeline/training/*.log
